{"id":542682,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/10/【图说天朝】上访老兵训诫书/","date":"2016-10-15T07:57:37Z","modified":"2016-10-15T07:57:37Z","title":"【图说天朝】上访老兵训诫书","content":"<blockquote><p>自由港 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/iyouport_news/status/787189835790446592\" target=\"_blank\">@iyouport_news</a>：到军委上访的老兵接受训诫。右图是昨晚的消息</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/Cuyo-iDVMAADc0w.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-542683\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/Cuyo-iDVMAADc0w.jpg\" alt=\"Cuyo-iDVMAADc0w\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/Cuyo-iDVMAADc0w.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/Cuyo-iDVMAADc0w-225x300.jpg 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>洛阳市公安局长春分局训诫书<br />\n&#8230;<br />\n天安门广场地区不是信访接待场所，不接待信访人员走访，也不允许信访人员滞留或聚集，你应到相关的信访接待部门去反映自己的问题。对违反上述规定，不听劝阻，情节严重的，公安机关将依据《中华人民共和国治安管理处罚法》等法律法规予以处理了。</p>\n<p>以上内容特此训诫。</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuvzMFVWAAAuMi9.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-542685\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuvzMFVWAAAuMi9.jpg\" alt=\"CuvzMFVWAAAuMi9\" width=\"475\" height=\"633\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuvzMFVWAAAuMi9.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuvzMFVWAAAuMi9-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuvzMFVWAAAuMi9-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 475px) 100vw, 475px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuvzMEUXgAELo3B.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-542684\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuvzMEUXgAELo3B.jpg\" alt=\"CuvzMEUXgAELo3B\" width=\"475\" height=\"633\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/10/CuvzMEUXgAELo3B.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/file